<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هَدْأة <span class="c4">[مفرد]</span>: ج هَدَآت وهَدْآت:<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١ - اسم مرَّة من هدَأَ/ هدَأَ بـ/ هدَأَ في.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
